# admin-resolve CLI run history — contains salts that are sensitive
# pre-reveal (front-runnable). Post-reveal they're public via on-chain
# logs anyway, so the local file is just for the operator's audit trail
# + cross-machine portability if they split commit and reveal.
tools/admin-resolve-history.json
